title: Wall Street is clearing its way back to its old highs, says Mercadien Asset Management's Ken Kamen

organizations.name: mercadien asset management's ken kamen wall street

text:
Wall Street is clearing its way back to its old highs, says Mercadien Asset Management's Ken Kamen Friday, February 23, 2018 - 03:58 
It will take time for U.S. stocks to get back up, for now the markets are trying to find a new level. Ken Kamen, president of Mercadien Asset Management. Aleksandra Michalska reports.
